Readme.md
# Bruhvoices Audio

Shared audio profiles and theme system for Bruhvoices.

## Audio profiles
- Standard Australian
- Warm Lesson
- Slow Practice
- Community-approved audio

## Notes
- Use Google TTS for standard voices.
- Keep community-approved audio behind separate approval metadata and playback.
- Do not imitate Indigenous identity or voices without rights-holder and community approval.




